717264f-a.text:

Broadway, east side, north from Broome Street. Note the Broadway surface car
April 19, 1935.

(2)
A detail of same, showing Nos. 502-04, 306, 508, 510, 512 and 516 (right to left). No. 506, the first low building was an old Dodd-Mead
retail store site.
April 19, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
(3)
A limited view, showing mainly No. 306.
April 19, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
